Figging
[[Image:Figging-movie-03.jpg|thumb|right|Figging in action]]
The classic definition of [[figging]] is the sexual act of inserting ginger into the [[anus]]. This has been expanded in modern times to also include insertion into the [[vagina]] or [[urethra]].

Figging prevents the figged from clenching their butt cheeks as this produces an extreme burning sensation. Due to this effect it is customary to cane the victim during the figging so you may see their ass cheeks bounce like a six-fo' filled with hotties. It is said that that figging was an accepted means of disciplining children in the Victorian era. This has been a major motivator behind [[NAMBLA]]'s investment in time travel research, second only to the ancient [[Greek]] practice of fucking [[shota|little boys]] like it was going out of style.

